{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8a377348e8","title":"许世友对毛泽东的汇报","origin":"1967年11月21日清华大学井冈山斗批改战团编印《学习资料》第48期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1899f38379","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":25,"articleId":"8a377348e8"}],"tags":[{"id":"c2f8307fbd","name":"许世友","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"cf3ac985fb","name":"许世友"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"b349510f04","type":"title","text":"许世友对毛泽东的汇报","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"073da30662","type":"authors","text":"许世友","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"aac53a1abf","type":"subtitle","text":"〖大意〗","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"3a93977476","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席八月二十五日在上海接见许世友同志。许世友同志向毛主席汇报了沿海战略部署情况。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"d13369cd4f","type":"paragraph","text":"然后许世友向毛主席汇报自己思想看法，说有三个不理解：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"a407b9cc3e","type":"paragraph","text":"一、这么多人（包括牛鬼蛇神）抢解放军的枪，我不理解。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"457122266e","type":"paragraph","text":"二、三大纪律八项注意到底管不管用，我不理解。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"56d1ffc0a6","type":"paragraph","text":"三、陈再道是什么人，我不理解。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"c41a897a92","type":"paragraph","text":"主席说：抢枪有好人抢，有坏人抢。好人抢了会认识错误，送回去。对坏人就要专政。三大纪律八项注意到底是管用的。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"ba5ba982d7","type":"paragraph","text":"许世友说：“现在为什么有人要夺我的枪？”","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"97628beba1","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席说：“顶多南京再出现一个张国焘。”","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"},{"id":"bf3cbb8ec6","type":"appellation","text":"","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8"}],"page":{"id":"11c0993775","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8a377348e8","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}